headline.main: Suspected U.S. Drones Hit Al Qaeda Targets in Yemen: Residents
headline.print_headline: Suspected U.S. Drones Hit Al Qaeda Targets in Yemen: Residents

lead_paragraph: Suspected U.S. drones fired missiles at al Qaeda targets in two separate attacks in Yemen on Monday, residents said, extending several days of U.S. strikes against the militants.
